Carol Vorderman, 62, was in fits of laughter as she wrestled behind the scenes at Taskmaster with host Greg Davies and singer Self Esteem, real name Rebecca Lucy Taylor. Carol reshared Rebecca's clip on Instagram along with the caption: "TASKMASTER WRESTLING... "Me. @selfesteemselfesteem and @gregdavies....Can't say who won @taskmaster. "Stonking great days....happy happy. Where was Alex [Horne] tho?" (sic) Carol appeared on the New Year episode of Taskmaster where she stunned in a bright red, figure-hugging jumpsuit.